4. Which region is expected to dominate the liquid vial filling machine market in the coming years?
North America is expected to dominate the market due to the presence of major pharmaceutical companies and technological advancements in vial filling machines.

5. What are the different types of liquid vial filling machines available in the market?
There are mainly three types of liquid vial filling machines: automatic vial filling machines, semi-automatic vial filling machines, and manual vial filling machines.

