Automatic vial filling machines hold the largest market share due to their higher efficiency and accuracy compared to manual and semi-automatic machines.

14. What are the factors influencing the adoption of liquid vial filling machines in the pharmaceutical industry?
The need for higher production capacity, stringent quality control, and the demand for sterile and aseptic vial filling processes are key factors influencing adoption in the pharmaceutical industry.

